data.description: This charming 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home has been recently updated. It features granite countertops, tile floors throughout the home, updated light fixtures, ceiling fans in the family room and all bedrooms, and 2" white faux wood blinds throughout the home.  There are nice size closets in the bedrooms and a spacious utility room. The main bathroom has also been updated recently with a spacious walk in shower and is handicap accessible.  The large back yard with covered patio is great for entertaining and there is a shed for extra storage space. The HVAC is one year old and the roof is 2 years old.  There is a tankless water heater and the washer, dryer, water softener and refrigerator convey.  This gem is a must see!
